articles.title: Abbott's all-round heroics take Australia to series win - Cricbuzz
articles.description: The all-rounder produced a fifty under pressure and then also picked up a three-fer
articles.content:
Sean Abbott made a telling impact with bat and ball to derail West Indies © Getty
Sean Abbott's all-round show (69 and 3-40) helped Australia prevail in the second ODI against West Indies at the SCG… [+2634 chars]
